stories.text: I created a VS code extension that simply displays in the status bar which Amplify environment you are currently working in. Also, if you change the Amplify environment, this extension will notify you with an information message. Please let me know what you think and if you find any bugs! This is my very first VS Code Extension so i am grateful for any input
